    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求欧洲购买美国武器以保持北约强大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情的欧洲官员透露，特朗普总统的政府已告诉英国和欧洲的盟友，希望他们购买美国武器和军事装备，以维护北约联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普最早将于 4 月实施对等关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-moves-to-impose-reciprocal-tariffs-but-not-right-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令其政府考虑对众多贸易伙伴征收对等关税，这增加了对全球体系发起更广泛攻击的可能性，他抱怨该体系对美国不利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-moves-to-impose-reciprocal-tariffs-but-not-right-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗与苏丹建立更深层次联系，扩大影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/iran-forges-deeper-ties-with-sudan-in-boost-to-wider-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹外交部称，伊朗和苏丹同意在采矿、银行和畜牧业生产领域进行合作，这引发了人们对伊朗伊斯兰共和国正在扩大其在中东边缘地区的影响力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/iran-forges-deeper-ties-with-sudan-in-boost-to-wider-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国高级将领称增加国防开支、人员至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/top-german-general-says-more-defense-spending-personnel-crucial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高级别士兵表示，德国迫切需要增加国防开支、扩大军队规模，以对抗俄罗斯的侵略，并减少对美国的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/top-german-general-says-more-defense-spending-personnel-crucial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯对特朗普的忠诚可能会破坏民主党的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-fealty-to-trump-risks-wrecking-democrat-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统的帮助，埃里克·亚当斯可能躲过了联邦腐败审判，但他们不太可能的联盟可能会破坏这位纽约市市长在核心民主党选民中的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/nyc-mayor-eric-adams-fealty-to-trump-risks-wrecking-democrat-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:12:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲对乌克兰问题的担忧加剧，斯塔默会见中国外长王毅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/starmer-meets-china-s-wang-as-europe-s-ukraine-concerns-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默周四在伦敦会见了中国外交部长王毅，尽管欧洲因唐纳德·特朗普干预俄罗斯乌克兰战争而感到震惊，但两国关系仍在缓和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/starmer-meets-china-s-wang-as-europe-s-ukraine-concerns-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街关于重新评估美国黄金价格的言论未能说服白宫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/wall-street-talk-of-revaluing-us-gold-isn-t-persuading-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金市场吸引了大量的边缘思想，最近几周其中一条思想 — — 美国应该重新评估其黄金储备 — — 已经牢牢抓住了华尔街的注意力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/wall-street-talk-of-revaluing-us-gold-isn-t-persuading-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:09:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯呼吁将国防开支提高至欧洲的 5%，但美国可能不需要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/hegseth-urges-5-defense-spending-for-europe-maybe-not-for-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯周四表示，欧洲的北约成员国应该承担更多的集体防御成本，这与唐纳德·特朗普总统要求盟友将 GDP 的 5% 用于国防的呼吁相呼应，同时回避了美国也应达到同一目标的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/hegseth-urges-5-defense-spending-for-europe-maybe-not-for-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 18:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党考虑去银行化之际，戴蒙敦促审查金融监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/banking-chiefs-to-talk-debanking-with-senate-banking-committee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司的杰米戴蒙支持重组美国金融监管机构，他周四在国会山表示，有必要“全面审视此事”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/banking-chiefs-to-talk-debanking-with-senate-banking-committee</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 13:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
